Release Notice and Licensing Terms
==================================

This repository packages research code together with a LoRA adapter for
scanpath prediction.

1. Code and LoRA adapter
   The evaluation code and the fine-tuned LoRA adapter weights
   (model/combined_adapter/) contained in this repository are released for
   NON-COMMERCIAL RESEARCH USE ONLY.

2. Base model
   This adapter is applied on top of the base model
   OpenGVLab/InternVL3_5-8B-HF, which is NOT distributed here and is pulled
   from HuggingFace at runtime. The base model is governed by its own upstream
   license, which you must review and accept on HuggingFace before use. Nothing
   in this notice grants you any rights to the base model weights.

3. Sample data
   The bundled MIT sample images (data/images/) and the derived center-bias
   priors (data/centerbias/) originate from the MIT / CAT2000-family
   eye-tracking datasets. They are included here solely as a small illustrative
   sample and remain subject to the original terms and conditions of those
   datasets. Consult the respective dataset providers for redistribution and
   usage terms.

THE SOFTWARE AND DATA ARE PROVIDED "AS IS", WITHOUT WARRANTY OF ANY KIND,
EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. THE AUTHORS SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY CLAIM, DAMAGES, OR
OTHER LIABILITY ARISING FROM THE USE OF THIS SOFTWARE OR DATA.
